@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ibwgzh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 0.10
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.46)) * 0.11)
    v0 = (v2 * v0)
    v0 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.17 * v2 + 0.91)) / wp.cos(v2))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.05 * v1 + 0.40)))
    data[tid] = v0
